headline: Why TaskUs Stock Soared on Friday
summary: TaskUs reported first-quarter results that beat analyst expectations on revenue and earnings.  Management canceled the expected earnings call after announcing a plan to take the company private.  Digital services provider TaskUs (NASDAQ: TASK) had a busy day on Friday.
